    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="guide"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#guide"></a> guide</h1><ol><li><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/371995929">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/371995929</a></li><li><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/juzaizai/p/14472119.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/juzaizai/p/14472119.html</a></li></ol><h1 id="theme"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#theme"></a> theme</h1><ul><li>next</li><li>fluid<ul><li><a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid</a></li><li>Hexo Fluid用戶手冊: <a href="https://fluid-dev.github.io/hexo-fluid-docs/guide/#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97">https://fluid-dev.github.io/hexo-fluid-docs/guide/#关于指南</a></li></ul></li></ul><h1 id="用法"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#用法"></a> 用法</h1><h2 id="基礎-粗體-引用塊-超連結"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#基礎-粗體-引用塊-超連結"></a> 基礎 (粗體、引用塊、超連結…)</h2><ol><li><a href="https://oldgerman.github.io/6c57f882/">hexo 博客如何写出彩色字体，能实时预览的那种？</a></li><li><a href="https://somelou.xyz/p/1136132855/#whereFont">hexo下的Mrakdown语法简册</a></li><li><a href="https://fengmumu1.github.io/2018/06/29/hexo-markdown-grammar/">hexo下的markdown语法</a></li></ol><h2 id="圖片"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#圖片"></a> 圖片</h2><p>Ref: <a href="https://blog.51cto.com/alexclownfish/3051079">https://blog.51cto.com/alexclownfish/3051079</a></p><ul><li>插入圖片，不可調整大小：  <div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs awk">![](<span class="hljs-regexp">/img/</span>example.jpg)![](https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>alexcld.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/images/</span>pengyuyan.jpg)</code></pre></div></li><li>插入圖片，可調整大小  <div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs awk">&lt;img src=<span class="hljs-regexp">/img/</span>pendulum.jpg width=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;30%&quot;</span> /&gt;<span class="hljs-comment"># 置中</span>&lt;center&gt;&lt;img src=<span class="hljs-regexp">/img/</span>pendulum.jpg width=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;30%&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-regexp">/&gt;&lt;/</span>center&gt;</code></pre></div></li></ul><h2 id="codeblock"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#codeblock"></a> codeblock</h2><p>Ref: <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/35441138/how-do-i-insert-this-code-into-a-hexo-markdown">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/35441138/how-do-i-insert-this-code-into-a-hexo-markdown</a></p><h2 id="數學公式"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#數學公式"></a> 數學公式</h2><h3 id="矩陣"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#矩陣"></a> 矩陣</h3><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/bendanban/article/details/44221279">https://blog.csdn.net/bendanban/article/details/44221279</a></p><h3 id="微分上面一點"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#微分上面一點"></a> 微分上面一點</h3><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs gams"><span class="hljs-symbol">$</span><span class="hljs-symbol">$</span>\dot&#123;x&#125;<span class="hljs-symbol">$</span><span class="hljs-symbol">$</span></code></pre></div><p>效果:</p><p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mover accent="true"><mi>x</mi><mo>˙</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dot{x}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.66786em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord accent"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.66786em;"><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span></span></span><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left:-0.11111000000000001em;">˙</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><h3 id="其他"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#其他"></a> 其他</h3><p><a href="http://yixin-oss.gitee.io/daytoy/2021/06/29/Hexo%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F/">http://yixin-oss.gitee.io/daytoy/2021/06/29/Hexo使用数学公式/</a></p><h3 id="留空行"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#留空行"></a> 留空行</h3><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-section">&lt;br/&gt;</span></code></pre></div><h2 id="特殊符號"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#特殊符號"></a> 特殊符號</h2><p><a href="http://yakinblog.com/2017/12/24/Markdown-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/">http://yakinblog.com/2017/12/24/Markdown-常用语法/</a></p><h1 id="problems-solve"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#problems-solve"></a> problems &amp; solve</h1><ul><li>hexo – 遠端更新<ul><li>hexo clean -&gt; hexo g -d</li></ul></li><li>hexo – po新文章，遠端不顯示<ul><li>等待(因為更新有延遲)</li><li>清除緩存 Crtl + F5</li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
